Intro:

Some basic Packer templates for generating Vagrant boxes.

Requirements:

Packer (>= 0.8 to use WinRM communicator with Windows templates)
Vagrant

Templates:

centos-7.json - Base install of CentOS 7.1.1503 x86_64
debian-8.1.0-amd64.json - Base install of Debian 8.1.0 amd64
ubuntu-15.04-server-amd64.json - Base install of Ubuntu Server 15.04 amd64
windows-10.json - Base install of Windows 10 Enterprise Evaluation

Usage:

git clone https://github.com/m-dwyer/packer-templates.git
cd packer-templates/
packer build $OS_NAME.json
vagrant box add boxes/$OS_NAME.box --name=$OS_NAME

vagrant init $OS_NAME
vagrant up
